---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Nanda Kishore">
  <Header />
  <main class="flex-1">
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-16">
        About Me
      </h1>
      
      <div class="space-y-8 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p class="mb-8">
          I'm an experienced DevOps professional with a passion for building robust, scalable cloud infrastructure. My expertise lies in architecting solutions that not only meet today's requirements but are designed to evolve and scale with growing business needs.
        </p>
        
        <p class="mb-8">
          As an Azure Cloud specialist, I navigate the Microsoft Azure ecosystem with confidence, leveraging its comprehensive suite of services to create efficient, cost-effective solutions. From infrastructure as code to container orchestration, I transform complex cloud challenges into streamlined, automated workflows.
        </p>
        
        <p class="mb-8">
          High availability and resilience aren't just buzzwords to me—they're fundamental principles that guide every system I design. I architect solutions with redundancy, failover mechanisms, and disaster recovery strategies built in from the ground up, ensuring that critical systems remain operational even when components fail.
        </p>
        
        <p class="mb-8">
          My expertise in cloud monitoring allows me to maintain complete visibility into system health, performance, and security. I implement comprehensive monitoring strategies that provide real-time insights, proactive alerting, and actionable intelligence—turning data into decisions that keep systems running smoothly and efficiently.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

